N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 64.3 - Vendors must be licensed

State Regulations

No retail licensee holding a license pursuant to section
63
or
64
of the Alcoholic Beverage Control Law, shall purchase, agree to purchase, acquire title to or receive in this State, any liquor described and identified by warehouse receipts, except if purchased
from the holder of a license pursuant to section
61
or
62
of the Alcoholic Beverage Control Law, and
as hereinafter provided. Notes
